parameters:
Taking care of the statues is tough... And I... I'm small and
petite...

La~la~... Taking care of flowers is the most enjoyable time for
me...

\SE[2]I thought you might know something. \!\SE[3]...How about
it?\. Do you have any idea?

Oh... This is something nostalgic you have there... I used to use
it a lot when I first started serving.

\SE[72]As expected, you're reliable...! \SE[2]Where is this key
from?

.........\.......\........ \!Just a moment... I will try to dig
it up from my memory somehow....
\SE[14]Please do your best! \.I don't have any other clues...!

Hmm... Cheers from a young woman... I don't mind... the pleasant
feeling...

Oh, I remembered...! It's the fountain! This is the key to the
fountain...!

\SE[72]Well done, Yard! \SE[20]...So what is this key to the
fountain!?

I-I might remember if I try... I'm not sure though... \!I'll
borrow the key then....
I'm certain... It should be here...

\SE[72]Well done! \SE\SE[3]...But it's only a matter of time
before this is exposed. \SE[3]Let's finish the search quickly.
